Testing
=======

Tests are written with Shoulda on top of Test::Unit and dummier for dummy app creation.  Tests are run using 'rake' or 'rake test' command.

1. Clone your fork git locally.
2. Install the dependencies
    $ bundle install
3. Create test app inside test/dummy of gem root.
    $ bundle exec dummier 
3. Run the tests:
    rake test
